{"tid":2365652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧再認證COVID-19源自中國 不排除武漢實驗室流出","createTime":"2021-01-14T02:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T04:41:47.000Z","uid":301479,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"92b5ec637c566595bad1c2fca638e7586cca4d8b","tid":2365652,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:49:32.000Z","msg":"[新頭殼newtalk] 「我們不知道COVID-19是不是從武漢實驗室流出，但所有證據都表明它從中國開始」，美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）在接受一家電台訪問時表示，目前還不知道問題的答案，因為中國共產黨當局1年多以來，一直拒絕外界進入調查，而且至少已經提出3種不同版本的理論「解釋」病毒來源。對於世界衛生組織（WHO）專家獲准入境中國調查，蓬佩奧則不表樂觀。"},{"pid":"13fe0479c9090fdb20f55781a7cf88ac456f651d","tid":2365652,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F677446457296420885%2F690471863515611156%2Fimage0.gif%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1RJvdOz9N-dj3Ul04RsF7eaTV2tn0CflqFrPL7d_VNxZgA6DZUlv3daxM&amp;h=58ada874&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"0ddba049ee015980209072e3c213d7bfa208f507","tid":2365652,"uid":8308,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:51:21.000Z","msg":"月尾<br />\n拜登: COVID-19源自美國 向廣大中國同胞道歉"},{"pid":"ba3460ef60e6c953f7e422e05d24e6cc8cebf85e","tid":2365652,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"13fe0479c9090fdb20f55781a7cf88ac456f651d","tid":2365652,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F677446457296420885%2F690471863515611156%2Fimage0.gif%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1RJvdOz9N-dj3Ul04RsF7eaTV2tn0CflqFrPL7d_VNxZgA6DZUlv3daxM&amp;h=58ada874&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hvtmrj3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvtmrj3.gif&h=d82214bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XH1rCrR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.